codex student community info session stanford law school stanford law school search utility navigation test directory news center library events publications contact & maps information for prospective students alumni employers current students faculty & staff calendar codex student community info session go back details february 2 2012 from 12 45 pm 2 00 pm stanford law school room 95 codex the stanford center for legal informatics would like to invite all stanford students to community building meeting so that we can learn about your interests in legal informatics and what the center can do for you the session will start off with short presentations by a few legal informatics startup companies and platforms from stanford and the community this will give you a chance to learn about some of the new technologies that are changing the field of law these developments will affect the nature legal profession in coming years and also offer you opportunities to approach your career in new and unconventional ways we will then have an informal discussion about your interests in the field so that we may better design future programs and talk for the stanford community lunch will be served registration is free and open to the public please click here to register contact robert lee rlee codex stanford edu admission please click here to register related stanford program in law science & technology codex stanford center for computers and law cloudy 51 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
